Class Enemy

  • java.lang.Object
    • operations.Enemy

  • public class Enemy
extends java.lang.Object
    this method is a wrapper class for the enemies you want to place on the screen this class allows you to track and to update the location and state of the enemy it holds a node which is the 3D box that represents the enemy on screen

    Liandri
